Class Hub

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.context.che.Hub
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModuleActivator, OntologyListener

    public class Hub
extends Object
implements OntologyListener, ModuleActivator
    Central class that takes care of starting and stopping application. It used to be the Activator class before splitting the OSGi logic.
